## Universal ISML Knowledge

### ISML Directive Reference

| ISML Directive | Purpose | React 19 + React Router 7 Equivalent |
|----------------|---------|--------------------------------------|
| `<isdecorate template="...">` | Layout wrapper | Handled by `_app.tsx` layout route |
| `<isinclude template="...">` | Static template include | `import Component from '@/components/...'` |
| `<isinclude url="${URLUtils.url(...)}">` | Remote/dynamic include | Loader data + `<Suspense>` + `<Await>` |
| `<isslot id="..." context="global">` | CMS content slot | `<Region>` component or direct API fetch |
| `<isloop items="${...}" var="item">` | Iteration | `{items.map(item => <Component key={...} />)}` |
| `<isif condition="${...}">` | Conditional | `{condition && <Component />}` or ternary |
| `<isprint value="${...}">` | Output (escaped) | `{value}` - JSX auto-escapes |
| `<isprint value="${...}" encoding="off">` | Raw HTML output | `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` (avoid if possible) |
| `<isset name="var" value="${...}">` | Variable assignment | JavaScript `const` or loader data |
| `<isscript>` | Server-side JS | Loader function or server component logic |
| `<iscontentasset aid="...">` | Content asset render | Fetch via CMS API, render in component |
| `${Resource.msg('key', 'bundle', null)}` | i18n string | `useTranslation()` from react-i18next |
| `${URLUtils.url('Controller-Action')}` | Route URL | `<Link to="/path">` or route path string |
| `${pdict.varName}` | Pipeline dictionary | `loaderData.varName` from loader |

### Slot Content Resolution

When you encounter `<isslot id="...">` in ISML, follow this resolution path:

1. **Find slot in `slots.xml`** by matching `slot-id` attribute
2. **Check `<template>` element** - this ISML file renders the slot content
3. **Check `<content>` element** - this defines the data source:
   - `<content-assets>` → Fetch content asset body via API
   - `<products>` → Fetch products via ShopperSearch/ShopperProducts API
   - `<categories>` → Fetch categories via ShopperProducts API
   - `<html>` → Inline HTML (use sparingly in React)

### Common Slot Templates

| Template | Purpose | React Approach |
|----------|---------|----------------|
| `contentAssetBody.isml` | Render CMS content asset HTML | Fetch asset, render body with `<div dangerouslySetInnerHTML>` or parse to components |
| `homePageProductSlot.isml` | Product tile grid | Fetch products in loader, render with `ProductTile` components |
| `htmlSlotContainer.isml` | Raw HTML from slot config | Avoid - parse content to structured data when possible |
| `categoryTile.isml` | Category navigation tiles | Fetch categories in loader, render with `CategoryTile` components |

