## Technology Requirements

All generated code MUST use:

| Category | Requirement | NO Alternatives |
|----------|-------------|-----------------|
| **Language** | TypeScript | No JavaScript, no Flow |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | No CSS modules, no styled-components, no Bootstrap |
| **Routing** | React Router 7 | File-based routes in `src/routes/` |
| **Data Loading** | React Router `loader` | Return promises for streaming SSR |
| **Streaming** | `<Suspense>` + `<Await>` | For progressive loading |
| **Components** | React Server Components (default) | Client components only when interactivity needed |
| **Interactive UI** | Radix UI primitives | No Bootstrap JS, no jQuery, no MUI |
| **Forms** | `useFetcher` + resource routes | Or `useActionState` for server actions |
| **State** | React Context + `useOptimistic` | No Redux, no Zustand, no MobX |
| **Animations** | CSS transitions + Tailwind | No Framer Motion (unless complex) |
| **API Access** | `@salesforce/storefront-next-runtime/scapi` | Via `createApiClients(context)` |

